[Cite as 312112003 Case Announcements, 2003-Ohio-1341.]

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS AND ADMINISTRATIVE ACTIONS

March 21, 2003

MERIT DECISIONS WITHOUT OPINIONS

2003-0016. In re Petition of the Office of Disciplinary Counsel for Disclosure of Evidence Presented to the Seneca Cty. Grand Jury in 2001.

This cause came on for consideration upon the filing of a petition of the Office of Disciplinary Counsel for disclosure of evidence presented to the Seneca County Grand Jury in 2001. Upon consideration thereof,

IT IS ORDERED by this court that the petition be, and hereby is, denied. It is further ordered that this matter be dismissed.

Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifee and O’Connor, JJ., concur. Moyer, C.J., Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., dissent.
